00:19:22.990 --> 00:19:27.280 align:middle line:84%
is nothing more than the
sum of all sentient beings

00:19:27.280 --> 00:19:30.180 align:middle line:84%
in this process of discovery,
of learning, and teaching.

00:19:30.180 --> 00:19:32.200 align:middle line:84%
We're all here to
do it together.

00:19:32.200 --> 00:19:34.700 align:middle line:90%
That's why this universe exists.

00:19:34.700 --> 00:19:37.180 align:middle line:84%
And to me, this
kind of revelation

00:19:37.180 --> 00:19:39.640 align:middle line:84%
brings tremendous
meaning and purpose

00:19:39.640 --> 00:19:40.983 align:middle line:90%
to each and every one of us.

00:19:40.983 --> 00:19:41.900 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: It sure does.

00:19:41.900 --> 00:19:44.170 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: And to
the very existence

00:19:44.170 --> 00:19:45.920 align:middle line:90%
of life in this universe.

00:19:45.920 --> 00:19:48.225 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: What is a soul to
you now at this point, Eben?

00:19:48.225 --> 00:19:49.600 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: I
think the best way

00:19:49.600 --> 00:19:53.950 align:middle line:84%
to define the soul is the soul
is what any individual sentient

00:19:53.950 --> 00:19:58.360 align:middle line:84%
being can come to see
is its direct eternal

00:19:58.360 --> 00:20:02.650 align:middle line:84%
of infinitely interconnected
aspect of knowing

00:20:02.650 --> 00:20:04.690 align:middle line:84%
through experience,
through learning,

00:20:04.690 --> 00:20:06.550 align:middle line:84%
through going through
an understanding,

00:20:06.550 --> 00:20:11.060 align:middle line:84%
through dealing with
hardships in this life.

00:20:11.060 --> 00:20:13.150 align:middle line:84%
I came from my journey
to see that hardships

00:20:13.150 --> 00:20:15.760 align:middle line:84%
and difficulties, illness
and injury are actually

00:20:15.760 --> 00:20:18.520 align:middle line:84%
the stepping stones
for our growth.

00:20:18.520 --> 00:20:22.990 align:middle line:84%
It's what leads us into
remembering the connectedness,

00:20:22.990 --> 00:20:26.200 align:middle line:84%
the love of that creative
force, for the creation, which

00:20:26.200 --> 00:20:29.380 align:middle line:84%
is basically our
relationship with our very

00:20:29.380 --> 00:20:30.760 align:middle line:84%
conscious awareness
and with that

00:20:30.760 --> 00:20:34.360 align:middle line:84%
God force at the
core of the universe

00:20:34.360 --> 00:20:36.175 align:middle line:84%
that so many have
come to realize.

00:20:36.175 --> 00:20:37.800 align:middle line:84%
Not just through
near-death experiences

00:20:37.800 --> 00:20:40.840 align:middle line:84%
and other spiritually
transformative experiences.

00:20:40.840 --> 00:20:43.990 align:middle line:84%
But cultivating that
through a program

00:20:43.990 --> 00:20:47.110 align:middle line:84%
of meditation with a purpose
of trying to learn more

00:20:47.110 --> 00:20:51.550 align:middle line:84%
about who am I, why am I
here, where is this all going,

00:20:51.550 --> 00:20:53.800 align:middle line:90%
how can I influence the outcome.

00:20:53.800 --> 00:20:57.100 align:middle line:84%
And each and every one of
us plays a tremendous role.

00:20:57.100 --> 00:21:00.400 align:middle line:84%
In fact, it's one thing that I
try and portray to every soul

00:21:00.400 --> 00:21:05.540 align:middle line:84%
that I encounter is
everyone is important.

00:21:05.540 --> 00:21:07.900 align:middle line:84%
There is no soul that
is unimportant in this.

00:21:07.900 --> 00:21:10.460 align:middle line:84%
And that includes a lot of the
naysayers and the doubters--

00:21:10.460 --> 00:21:11.260 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: True.

00:21:11.260 --> 00:21:13.090 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: --because
they actually

00:21:13.090 --> 00:21:16.750 align:middle line:84%
present a very important
kind of viewpoint.

00:21:16.750 --> 00:21:20.620 align:middle line:84%
And from my point of view,
as I often say in my talks,

00:21:20.620 --> 00:21:24.070 align:middle line:84%
the best ally in this
journey of deep discovery

00:21:24.070 --> 00:21:26.320 align:middle line:84%
of trying to understand
the nature of consciousness

00:21:26.320 --> 00:21:31.120 align:middle line:84%
and existence is a true
open-minded skepticism.

00:21:31.120 --> 00:21:34.508 align:middle line:84%
Doubt everything, right
down to ground level.

00:21:34.508 --> 00:21:35.800 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: But have an open mind.

00:21:35.800 --> 00:21:37.930 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: But have
a very open mind.

00:21:37.930 --> 00:21:39.100 align:middle line:90%
And that is the gift.

00:21:39.100 --> 00:21:41.530 align:middle line:84%
And, in fact, I will
tell you in a discussion

00:21:41.530 --> 00:21:43.870 align:middle line:84%
of the brain/mind
relationship, which

00:21:43.870 --> 00:21:47.020 align:middle line:84%
you can look at as a linear
spectrum, with materialism--

00:21:47.020 --> 00:21:50.080 align:middle line:84%
my conventional
view before coma--

00:21:50.080 --> 00:21:52.750 align:middle line:84%
physical world is all
that exists, therefore,

00:21:52.750 --> 00:21:55.000 align:middle line:84%
the brain must somehow
create consciousness.

00:21:55.000 --> 00:21:56.830 align:middle line:90%
That's one end of the spectrum.

00:21:56.830 --> 00:21:58.450 align:middle line:84%
Then you've got all
these dualities,

00:21:58.450 --> 00:22:01.210 align:middle line:84%
just as Penfield and many
others have observed.

00:22:01.210 --> 00:22:03.783 align:middle line:84%
You cannot reduce
mind to brains.

00:22:03.783 --> 00:22:05.200 align:middle line:84%
So they say, OK,
there's something

00:22:05.200 --> 00:22:07.690 align:middle line:84%
about mind and something
about brain and they coexist.

00:22:07.690 --> 00:22:09.670 align:middle line:84%
And you've got all these
dualistic positions

00:22:09.670 --> 00:22:10.640 align:middle line:90%
in philosophy.

00:22:10.640 --> 00:22:12.370 align:middle line:84%
But at the far end
of the spectrum

00:22:12.370 --> 00:22:15.160 align:middle line:84%
is metaphysical or
ontological idealism.

00:22:15.160 --> 00:22:17.930 align:middle line:84%
That is, that it's
a mental universe.

00:22:17.930 --> 00:22:20.290 align:middle line:84%
And, in fact, that's a
very comfortable idea

00:22:20.290 --> 00:22:21.370 align:middle line:90%
for quantum physicists.

00:22:21.370 --> 00:22:25.030 align:middle line:84%
For example, I would steer
the scientifically-minded

00:22:25.030 --> 00:22:28.340 align:middle line:84%
in your audience
to look at nature.

00:22:28.340 --> 00:22:33.880 align:middle line:84%
2005-- Richard Conn Henry, who
is the head of astrophysics

00:22:33.880 --> 00:22:36.770 align:middle line:84%
at Johns Hopkins
University-- very--

00:22:36.770 --> 00:22:37.570 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Astute.

00:22:37.570 --> 00:22:40.270 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: --renowned
and astute scientist.

00:22:40.270 --> 00:22:43.630 align:middle line:10%
He wrote a one-page essay
on the mental universe where

00:22:43.630 --> 00:22:45.910 align:middle line:10%
he made it very clear
that what is emerging

00:22:45.910 --> 00:22:48.100 align:middle line:10%
in the world of quantum
physics and in understanding

00:22:48.100 --> 00:22:52.030 align:middle line:10%
of it is just as those
founding fathers, like Erwin

00:22:52.030 --> 00:22:55.840 align:middle line:10%
Schrodinger, and Wolfgang
Pauli, and Eugene Wigner,

00:22:55.840 --> 00:22:57.610 align:middle line:10%
and others said.

00:22:57.610 --> 00:22:59.030 align:middle line:90%
Mind is fundamental.

00:22:59.030 --> 00:23:01.390 align:middle line:90%
Mind is at the base of it all.

00:23:01.390 --> 00:23:04.220 align:middle line:90%
Mind generates matter.

00:23:04.220 --> 00:23:07.000 align:middle line:84%
And they were very sure of that,
even with those early quantum

00:23:07.000 --> 00:23:07.800 align:middle line:90%
experiments.

00:23:07.800 --> 00:23:11.500 align:middle line:84%
And those experiments have only
gotten more and more refined.

00:23:11.500 --> 00:23:13.150 align:middle line:84%
But what they are
all trying to tell

00:23:13.150 --> 00:23:15.460 align:middle line:90%
us is that mind is fundamental.

00:23:15.460 --> 00:23:17.170 align:middle line:90%
We live in a mental universe.

00:23:17.170 --> 00:23:20.800 align:middle line:84%
And anybody who questions
mind over matter

00:23:20.800 --> 00:23:24.340 align:middle line:84%
and the reality of it, I'd say,
well, look at placebo effect.

00:23:24.340 --> 00:23:28.180 align:middle line:84%
The medical profession has
known for more than six decades

00:23:28.180 --> 00:23:33.530 align:middle line:84%
that the placebo effect is a
very nice, a powerful standard

00:23:33.530 --> 00:23:34.330 align:middle line:90%
to assess it.

00:23:34.330 --> 00:23:34.870 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: It's real.

00:23:34.870 --> 00:23:36.037 align:middle line:90%
>>ALEXANDER: It's very real.

00:23:36.037 --> 00:23:37.810 align:middle line:90%
And it assesses new treatments.

00:23:37.810 --> 00:23:41.350 align:middle line:84%
Not only medicines,
but also procedures.

00:23:41.350 --> 00:23:43.630 align:middle line:84%
There was a recent study
of stenting in the coronary

00:23:43.630 --> 00:23:48.280 align:middle line:84%
arteries in Britain that use
a placebo, a sham procedure,

00:23:48.280 --> 00:23:51.790 align:middle line:84%
to reveal that what we thought
was so solid-- that is,

00:23:51.790 --> 00:23:54.478 align:middle line:84%
coronary stents to
relieve angina--

00:23:54.478 --> 00:23:56.020 align:middle line:84%
was all a matter of
mind over matter.

00:23:56.020 --> 00:23:56.380 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: That's amazing.

00:23:56.380 --> 00:23:57.850 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: That,
in fact, placebo

00:23:57.850 --> 00:24:00.340 align:middle line:84%
was easily as good
as the results

00:24:00.340 --> 00:24:01.800 align:middle line:90%
of the procedure itself.

00:24:01.800 --> 00:24:04.540 align:middle line:84%
Now, and some people
misinterpret placebo.

00:24:04.540 --> 00:24:06.490 align:middle line:84%
They think, oh, you're
just fooling somebody.

00:24:06.490 --> 00:24:07.480 align:middle line:90%
You give them a sugar pill.

00:24:07.480 --> 00:24:08.290 align:middle line:90%
Tell them they get better.

00:24:08.290 --> 00:24:09.748 align:middle line:84%
And they get rid
of their headache.

00:24:09.748 --> 00:24:12.410 align:middle line:10%
Well, I would urge you
to look on the Institute

00:24:12.410 --> 00:24:15.370 align:middle line:10%
of Noetic Sciences website.

00:24:15.370 --> 00:24:20.020 align:middle line:10%
In the mid-1990s, they
assembled more than 3,500 cases

00:24:20.020 --> 00:24:23.620 align:middle line:10%
of miraculous healing,
spontaneous regression

00:24:23.620 --> 00:24:26.860 align:middle line:10%
of cancers, of advanced
infections, even

00:24:26.860 --> 00:24:31.540 align:middle line:10%
of congenital deformities, of
degenerative diseases, where

00:24:31.540 --> 00:24:33.370 align:middle line:10%
they showed that a
patient believing

00:24:33.370 --> 00:24:35.860 align:middle line:10%
they were doing something
that could make them better

00:24:35.860 --> 00:24:38.650 align:middle line:10%
would basically
make them better.

00:24:38.650 --> 00:24:43.600 align:middle line:84%
And what I can say about that is
that our modern medical schools

00:24:43.600 --> 00:24:45.730 align:middle line:84%
are finally catching
up on all this

00:24:45.730 --> 00:24:49.240 align:middle line:84%
and realizing that that
old materialist science--

00:24:49.240 --> 00:24:51.460 align:middle line:84%
the chemistry, and the
physics, and the biology that

00:24:51.460 --> 00:24:52.870 align:middle line:90%
was taught in medical schools--

00:24:52.870 --> 00:24:55.270 align:middle line:84%
and tried to pretend
that it was all just

00:24:55.270 --> 00:24:59.230 align:middle line:84%
the interaction of molecules
and nothing more is false.

00:24:59.230 --> 00:25:01.880 align:middle line:84%
That, in fact, a tremendous
amount of healing--

00:25:01.880 --> 00:25:05.230 align:middle line:84%
I mean, you can demonstrate
all of this as has been done.

00:25:05.230 --> 00:25:07.690 align:middle line:84%
The big question in my
mind is how much of what

00:25:07.690 --> 00:25:11.110 align:middle line:84%
we see and attribute
to medicines

00:25:11.110 --> 00:25:13.420 align:middle line:84%
that move beyond
that placebo effect

00:25:13.420 --> 00:25:16.100 align:middle line:84%
is actually just placebo
effect in disguise.

00:25:16.100 --> 00:25:17.642 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: That's an
interesting thing.

00:25:17.642 --> 00:25:19.900 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: I mean, we
already know that free will,

00:25:19.900 --> 00:25:20.920 align:middle line:90%
power of prayer--

00:25:20.920 --> 00:25:23.590 align:middle line:84%
there are many ways to
influence and interact

00:25:23.590 --> 00:25:26.620 align:middle line:84%
with this primordial mind
that is the determinant

00:25:26.620 --> 00:25:28.810 align:middle line:90%
of our evolving reality.

00:25:28.810 --> 00:25:30.760 align:middle line:84%
And that's why
developing a relationship

00:25:30.760 --> 00:25:33.850 align:middle line:84%
with that primordial
mind, that God force,

00:25:33.850 --> 00:25:37.490 align:middle line:84%
is so important for all of us
for very practical reasons.

00:25:37.490 --> 00:25:39.860 align:middle line:84%
And our health is right
at the top of that list.

00:25:39.860 --> 00:25:40.780 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: It sure is.

00:25:40.780 --> 00:25:43.300 align:middle line:84%
Psychic medium James
Van Praagh, of course,

00:25:43.300 --> 00:25:46.280 align:middle line:84%
has talked about the
power of the soul.

00:25:46.280 --> 00:25:47.080 align:middle line:90%
Truly remarkable.

00:25:47.080 --> 00:25:47.880 align:middle line:90%
