00:25:47.880 --> 00:25:51.540 align:middle line:10%
- The number one overall lesson,
whether positive or negative,

00:25:51.540 --> 00:25:52.960 align:middle line:10%
is love.

00:25:52.960 --> 00:25:55.270 align:middle line:10%
Number one, we have to
learn to love ourselves,

00:25:55.270 --> 00:25:58.390 align:middle line:10%
to really embrace ourselves,
to honor ourselves,

00:25:58.390 --> 00:25:59.860 align:middle line:10%
and to forgive ourselves.

00:25:59.860 --> 00:26:01.530 align:middle line:10%
Very difficult sometimes.

00:26:01.530 --> 00:26:03.670 align:middle line:10%
But how can you
love another person

00:26:03.670 --> 00:26:05.300 align:middle line:10%
if you don't love
yourself first?

00:26:05.300 --> 00:26:07.870 align:middle line:10%
So we must learn the
various aspects of love

00:26:07.870 --> 00:26:09.910 align:middle line:10%
and loving those
parts of ourselves

00:26:09.910 --> 00:26:13.830 align:middle line:10%
which perhaps we perceive
as negative or not full.

00:26:13.830 --> 00:26:16.150 align:middle line:10%
We have to love every
aspect of ourselves

00:26:16.150 --> 00:26:18.040 align:middle line:10%
and then we're able
to love somebody else.

00:26:18.040 --> 00:26:20.560 align:middle line:10%
Love is an incredible energy.

00:26:20.560 --> 00:26:24.050 align:middle line:10%
Love is the number one energy,
the vibration of the universe.

00:26:24.050 --> 00:26:27.690 align:middle line:10%
And that is really what we
want to align ourselves toward.

00:26:27.690 --> 00:26:29.290 align:middle line:10%
We are all trying
to bring us back

00:26:29.290 --> 00:26:32.320 align:middle line:10%
to that oneness-- that oneness
of love is what we all are.

00:26:32.320 --> 00:26:34.270 align:middle line:10%
And so we come back
in these lifetimes--

00:26:34.270 --> 00:26:37.030 align:middle line:10%
this all comes back from
lifetime to lifetime,

00:26:37.030 --> 00:26:39.700 align:middle line:10%
from experience to
experience, from one world

00:26:39.700 --> 00:26:42.730 align:middle line:10%
to another world, to experience
the various aspects of love

00:26:42.730 --> 00:26:45.230 align:middle line:10%
and to share that aspect of
love with everybody else.

00:26:45.230 --> 00:26:46.030 align:middle line:90%
[END PLAYBACK]

