cure yourself on things.

00:26:52.840 --> 00:26:54.680 align:middle line:90%
>>ALEXANDER: That's very much--

00:26:54.680 --> 00:26:55.540 align:middle line:90%
very real.

00:26:55.540 --> 00:26:56.820 align:middle line:90%
I mean, I love this--

00:26:56.820 --> 00:26:59.290 align:middle line:84%
I know I've said in my
book, "Proof of Heaven,"

00:26:59.290 --> 00:27:03.190 align:middle line:84%
I said the deepest scientific
truth of my journey

00:27:03.190 --> 00:27:07.090 align:middle line:84%
was the discovery of the power
of the binding force of love.

00:27:07.090 --> 00:27:08.170 align:middle line:90%
And how we're all bound--

00:27:08.170 --> 00:27:08.530 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: So true.

00:27:08.530 --> 00:27:10.072 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: --together
through that.

00:27:10.072 --> 00:27:13.960 align:middle line:84%
And really the best way
to manifest love for self

00:27:13.960 --> 00:27:16.630 align:middle line:84%
is to serve as a
conduit, to allow

00:27:16.630 --> 00:27:20.080 align:middle line:84%
that love to flow
through, and love others.

00:27:20.080 --> 00:27:22.660 align:middle line:84%
Kindness, compassion,
forgiveness

00:27:22.660 --> 00:27:25.570 align:middle line:84%
when necessary,
gratitude for all

00:27:25.570 --> 00:27:27.670 align:middle line:84%
those beautiful relationships
we have with people.

00:27:27.670 --> 00:27:29.920 align:middle line:84%
And that includes the
tough relationships,

00:27:29.920 --> 00:27:32.410 align:middle line:84%
because they are often
there to serve, again,

00:27:32.410 --> 00:27:34.665 align:middle line:84%
just like hardships,
like illness, and injury,

00:27:34.665 --> 00:27:36.040 align:middle line:84%
the tough
relationships are there

00:27:36.040 --> 00:27:38.500 align:middle line:90%
to help guide us, to learn more.

00:27:38.500 --> 00:27:42.250 align:middle line:84%
And the more we can live our
lives with love in our heart,

00:27:42.250 --> 00:27:45.460 align:middle line:84%
love for self, love for
others, the more this world

00:27:45.460 --> 00:27:46.390 align:middle line:90%
will change.

00:27:46.390 --> 00:27:50.200 align:middle line:84%
One of the profound lessons
of my near-death experience

00:27:50.200 --> 00:27:55.510 align:middle line:84%
was coming to see that those
hardships and difficulties

00:27:55.510 --> 00:28:00.520 align:middle line:84%
truly are the pathway
towards becoming

00:28:00.520 --> 00:28:04.180 align:middle line:84%
more of who we are here to
be, and that love is really

00:28:04.180 --> 00:28:05.060 align:middle line:90%
the key.

00:28:05.060 --> 00:28:07.870 align:middle line:84%
And of course, the empirical
data for the power of love

00:28:07.870 --> 00:28:10.000 align:middle line:84%
comes from near-death
experiences, which

00:28:10.000 --> 00:28:12.700 align:middle line:84%
are independent of
your religious beliefs,

00:28:12.700 --> 00:28:15.010 align:middle line:90%
of your cultural beliefs.

00:28:15.010 --> 00:28:18.190 align:middle line:84%
They have a commonality of
the binding force of love

00:28:18.190 --> 00:28:21.730 align:middle line:84%
going back thousands of
years across all continents.

00:28:21.730 --> 00:28:24.710 align:middle line:84%
And the more scientists
study near-death experiences,

00:28:24.710 --> 00:28:27.340 align:middle line:84%
the more they come to realize
that a very deep lesson

00:28:27.340 --> 00:28:30.640 align:middle line:84%
about the nature of reality
is that that love is

00:28:30.640 --> 00:28:31.760 align:middle line:90%
the most important thing.

00:28:31.760 --> 00:28:35.170 align:middle line:84%
In fact, for me, it became
very clear after my coma

00:28:35.170 --> 00:28:38.800 align:middle line:84%
that this is not a battle
between good and evil.

00:28:38.800 --> 00:28:41.650 align:middle line:84%
The forces of darkness
maybe being powerful enough

00:28:41.650 --> 00:28:44.350 align:middle line:84%
to someday overwhelm the
forces of light and love.

00:28:44.350 --> 00:28:48.610 align:middle line:84%
Because that apparent darkness,
the apparent evil in our world,

00:28:48.610 --> 00:28:53.230 align:middle line:84%
is really the absence
of the light and love.

00:28:53.230 --> 00:28:55.240 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Well, when
you talk about evil,

00:28:55.240 --> 00:28:58.570 align:middle line:84%
I think back at the horrendous
things that Hitler did

00:28:58.570 --> 00:29:03.730 align:middle line:84%
or Joseph Stalin for the
Soviet Union at the time.

00:29:03.730 --> 00:29:04.990 align:middle line:90%
How does the planet--

00:29:04.990 --> 00:29:08.750 align:middle line:84%
how does the universe
compensate for people like that?

00:29:08.750 --> 00:29:13.570 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: Well, I think
that's a complicated question

00:29:13.570 --> 00:29:14.370 align:middle line:90%
in many ways.

00:29:14.370 --> 00:29:17.120 align:middle line:84%
But in some ways,
it's also simple.

00:29:17.120 --> 00:29:20.840 align:middle line:84%
If you use the analogy of look
at the world of, say, addiction

00:29:20.840 --> 00:29:23.870 align:middle line:84%
and alcoholism, we
often talk about what's

00:29:23.870 --> 00:29:26.300 align:middle line:90%
called a gift of desperation.

00:29:26.300 --> 00:29:28.100 align:middle line:84%
And it's because
when you're wrestling

00:29:28.100 --> 00:29:31.940 align:middle line:84%
with these kinds of issues, you
circle the drain and head down,

00:29:31.940 --> 00:29:35.180 align:middle line:84%
and sooner or later you
realize that you're either

00:29:35.180 --> 00:29:37.660 align:middle line:84%
going to have to come to some
truth with yourself about

00:29:37.660 --> 00:29:40.160 align:middle line:84%
things and start learning the
lessons the universe is trying

00:29:40.160 --> 00:29:43.130 align:middle line:84%
to give you or you're
going to come to an end.

00:29:43.130 --> 00:29:47.630 align:middle line:84%
And unfortunately, in alcoholism
and addiction, in many cases

00:29:47.630 --> 00:29:50.060 align:middle line:84%
in our modern
world, which I think

00:29:50.060 --> 00:29:53.870 align:middle line:84%
is so seduced by the
false sense of separation

00:29:53.870 --> 00:29:56.240 align:middle line:84%
of scientific
materialism that we

00:29:56.240 --> 00:29:59.540 align:middle line:84%
start believing that business
of our ego and the demands

00:29:59.540 --> 00:30:01.520 align:middle line:90%
that our ego makes on us.

00:30:01.520 --> 00:30:04.130 align:middle line:84%
And that includes
massive consumerism,

00:30:04.130 --> 00:30:06.650 align:middle line:84%
economic polarization,
things like that that

00:30:06.650 --> 00:30:09.260 align:middle line:90%
are very toxic, very damaging.

00:30:09.260 --> 00:30:14.240 align:middle line:84%
Because it really is about
more realizing that oneness,

00:30:14.240 --> 00:30:18.200 align:middle line:84%
and that connectedness, and that
it's what we do for ourselves

00:30:18.200 --> 00:30:21.830 align:middle line:84%
and others that gives to
the higher good that I think

00:30:21.830 --> 00:30:24.470 align:middle line:84%
can really take us in
a beautiful direction.

00:30:24.470 --> 00:30:27.950 align:middle line:84%
I came to realize that
unconditional love has

00:30:27.950 --> 00:30:30.050 align:middle line:90%
infinite power to heal.

00:30:30.050 --> 00:30:33.780 align:middle line:84%
And to me, that was one
of the biggest indicators

00:30:33.780 --> 00:30:36.620 align:middle line:84%
of how all this is
working out with evil, why

00:30:36.620 --> 00:30:38.240 align:middle line:90%
there can be so much evil.

00:30:38.240 --> 00:30:42.163 align:middle line:84%
Because no one doubts the
tremendous amount of darkness

00:30:42.163 --> 00:30:43.580 align:middle line:84%
and evil in our
world, even though

00:30:43.580 --> 00:30:46.250 align:middle line:84%
I believe that it's
improving rapidly.

00:30:46.250 --> 00:30:49.940 align:middle line:10%
I believe the awakening that
many of us in consciousness

00:30:49.940 --> 00:30:52.820 align:middle line:10%
studies talk about from
a scientific viewpoint is

00:30:52.820 --> 00:30:55.040 align:middle line:10%
inevitable, in one
sense, but also,

00:30:55.040 --> 00:30:59.258 align:middle line:10%
absolutely crucial if we
are to survive as a species.

00:30:59.258 --> 00:31:00.800 align:middle line:84%
This is something
we talk about a lot

00:31:00.800 --> 00:31:02.420 align:middle line:84%
in "Living in a
Mindful Universe."

00:31:02.420 --> 00:31:05.000 align:middle line:84%
I think it's the reason
this awakening is happening.

00:31:05.000 --> 00:31:07.520 align:middle line:84%
So in essence, these
kinds of challenges,

00:31:07.520 --> 00:31:09.320 align:middle line:84%
this apparent darkness
and evil that we

00:31:09.320 --> 00:31:12.110 align:middle line:84%
see of humans
against other humans,

00:31:12.110 --> 00:31:14.780 align:middle line:84%
is really that gift
of desperation.

00:31:14.780 --> 00:31:17.720 align:middle line:84%
And we can come to our senses
and wake up to the reality

00:31:17.720 --> 00:31:22.670 align:middle line:84%
of this, because the status quo,
especially with any apparent

00:31:22.670 --> 00:31:25.760 align:middle line:84%
overwhelming nature of that
selfishness, and greediness,

00:31:25.760 --> 00:31:29.240 align:middle line:84%
and the economic polarization,
the damage to the climate from

00:31:29.240 --> 00:31:31.700 align:middle line:84%
the material excesses,
fossil fuel addiction--

00:31:31.700 --> 00:31:32.810 align:middle line:90%
what have you--

00:31:32.810 --> 00:31:36.110 align:middle line:84%
is all something that can
come into a much finer balance

00:31:36.110 --> 00:31:39.260 align:middle line:84%
when we recover this oneness
of connection, binding

00:31:39.260 --> 00:31:42.080 align:middle line:84%
force of love, and realize
that we're really all here

00:31:42.080 --> 00:31:43.400 align:middle line:90%
to help each other.

00:31:43.400 --> 00:31:45.380 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Where does
prayer fit into this?

00:31:45.380 --> 00:31:48.200 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: Well, from my point
of view, prayer and meditation

00:31:48.200 --> 00:31:50.390 align:middle line:90%
in many ways are the same thing.

00:31:50.390 --> 00:31:52.460 align:middle line:84%
And certainly, the
way I use meditation.

00:31:52.460 --> 00:31:54.530 align:middle line:84%
I use sacred acoustics
to get into very

00:31:54.530 --> 00:31:57.710 align:middle line:84%
deep transcendental states
of awareness, which to me are

00:31:57.710 --> 00:31:59.960 align:middle line:90%
a form of centering prayer.

00:31:59.960 --> 00:32:03.320 align:middle line:84%
And centering prayer is really
a form of silent prayer.

00:32:03.320 --> 00:32:07.910 align:middle line:84%
It's not going in and
asking for things, other

00:32:07.910 --> 00:32:11.660 align:middle line:84%
than that thy will, that
the higher good be served.

00:32:11.660 --> 00:32:14.930 align:middle line:84%
And especially, when you
start to realize how important

00:32:14.930 --> 00:32:17.840 align:middle line:84%
it is to get the bigger
picture of your existence

00:32:17.840 --> 00:32:19.863 align:middle line:84%
through an acknowledgment
of reincarnation.

00:32:19.863 --> 00:32:21.530 align:middle line:84%
That you've been here
many times before.

00:32:21.530 --> 00:32:26.060 align:middle line:84%
That you're in a progressive
growth phase of learning that

00:32:26.060 --> 00:32:28.150 align:middle line:90%
involves other future lifetimes.

00:32:28.150 --> 00:32:30.920 align:middle line:84%
That your relationships
with people in this lifetime

00:32:30.920 --> 00:32:33.230 align:middle line:84%
are simply reshuffling
of relationships

00:32:33.230 --> 00:32:35.720 align:middle line:84%
with similar souls
in prior lifetimes,

00:32:35.720 --> 00:32:37.490 align:middle line:84%
and that you're all
working together

00:32:37.490 --> 00:32:40.010 align:middle line:84%
toward something bigger
in future lifetimes,

00:32:40.010 --> 00:32:43.130 align:middle line:84%
gives us an ability
to see that prayer,

00:32:43.130 --> 00:32:45.920 align:middle line:84%
opening up to this oneness
of that creative force

00:32:45.920 --> 00:32:48.140 align:middle line:84%
of the universe, that
God force, coming

00:32:48.140 --> 00:32:51.350 align:middle line:84%
to realize our alignment
with that force,

00:32:51.350 --> 00:32:54.480 align:middle line:84%
having love in our hearts,
love and compassion,

00:32:54.480 --> 00:32:56.600 align:middle line:90%
kindness for self and others.

00:32:56.600 --> 00:32:59.660 align:middle line:84%
And that is something that
can be easily involved

00:32:59.660 --> 00:33:03.050 align:middle line:84%
in a prayerful state
of seeking the highest

00:33:03.050 --> 00:33:04.970 align:middle line:90%
and best good for all involved.

00:33:04.970 --> 00:33:07.490 align:middle line:84%
I see many examples
of how prayer

00:33:07.490 --> 00:33:10.250 align:middle line:84%
has been very powerful
in people's lives to help

00:33:10.250 --> 00:33:12.110 align:middle line:90%
give them the outcome needed.

00:33:12.110 --> 00:33:14.900 align:middle line:84%
That doesn't always mean
you get physical healing.

00:33:14.900 --> 00:33:16.970 align:middle line:84%
Although, in so
many cases it does.

00:33:16.970 --> 00:33:19.280 align:middle line:84%
And we've already talked
about mind over matter,

00:33:19.280 --> 00:33:22.130 align:middle line:84%
in general, and the
placebo effect and all

00:33:22.130 --> 00:33:23.880 align:middle line:90%
of those spontaneous remissions.

00:33:23.880 --> 00:33:27.380 align:middle line:84%
But I would say the
biggest example of that

00:33:27.380 --> 00:33:29.220 align:middle line:90%
is in near-death experiences.

00:33:29.220 --> 00:33:30.740 align:middle line:84%
For example, that
case report that I

00:33:30.740 --> 00:33:33.320 align:middle line:84%
talked about a little
while ago of my case.

00:33:33.320 --> 00:33:38.270 align:middle line:84%
Those physicians remarked
on not only the surprise

00:33:38.270 --> 00:33:40.700 align:middle line:84%
that I would have any
conscious experience at all,

00:33:40.700 --> 00:33:43.430 align:middle line:84%
but they even go so
far as to surmise

00:33:43.430 --> 00:33:45.200 align:middle line:84%
that one of the
reasons that I had

00:33:45.200 --> 00:33:48.248 align:middle line:84%
such a remarkable
recovery-- and no doctor who

00:33:48.248 --> 00:33:49.790 align:middle line:84%
looks at my medical
records and looks

00:33:49.790 --> 00:33:52.970 align:middle line:84%
at how I've come out of it all,
would doubt that it's really

00:33:52.970 --> 00:33:55.910 align:middle line:84%
a miracle, it has no explanation
within Western medicine--

00:33:55.910 --> 00:33:59.000 align:middle line:84%
but you actually find
that kind of healing all

00:33:59.000 --> 00:34:00.380 align:middle line:90%
through the NDE literature.

00:34:00.380 --> 00:34:05.150 align:middle line:84%
For example, Mary C. Neal,
the orthopedic surgeon who had

00:34:05.150 --> 00:34:08.330 align:middle line:84%
a near-death experience
kayaking in Chile--

00:34:08.330 --> 00:34:09.889 align:middle line:90%
late 1990s.

00:34:09.889 --> 00:34:12.920 align:middle line:84%
Her kayak went under water more
than 10 feet, broke her legs,

00:34:12.920 --> 00:34:15.070 align:middle line:84%
buried her under
water for 30 minutes.

00:34:15.070 --> 00:34:15.949 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: She couldn't get
out of the kayak, right?

00:34:15.949 --> 00:34:18.050 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: Yeah, she was stuck
with broken legs in the kayak,

00:34:18.050 --> 00:34:19.820 align:middle line:84%
more than 30
minutes under water.

00:34:19.820 --> 00:34:20.650 align:middle line:90%
You don't come back from that.

00:34:20.650 --> 00:34:20.929 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: No.

00:34:20.929 --> 00:34:21.729 align:middle line:90%
Nobody does.

00:34:21.729 --> 00:34:24.530 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: But she
did because of the power

00:34:24.530 --> 00:34:26.760 align:middle line:84%
of the spiritual
nature of an NDE,

00:34:26.760 --> 00:34:29.030 align:middle line:84%
which is the same as
the power of prayer,

00:34:29.030 --> 00:34:30.389 align:middle line:90%
it helped her to come back.

00:34:30.389 --> 00:34:33.830 align:middle line:84%
And I think, similarly, in
the case of Anita Moorjani.

00:34:33.830 --> 00:34:36.080 align:middle line:84%
She wrote the book
"Dying to Be Me."

00:34:36.080 --> 00:34:40.310 align:middle line:10%
And she had a very advanced
lymphoma back in February 2006.

00:34:40.310 --> 00:34:43.820 align:middle line:84%
Taken into a hospital room, in
emergency room in Hong Kong.

00:34:43.820 --> 00:34:46.380 align:middle line:84%
Any doctor on Earth would
look at her medical facts

00:34:46.380 --> 00:34:48.630 align:middle line:84%
at that moment, say she'll
be dead within eight hours,

00:34:48.630 --> 00:34:49.430 align:middle line:90%
no doubt.

00:34:49.430 --> 00:34:50.239 align:middle line:90%
Well, she's not.

00:34:50.239 --> 00:34:51.050 align:middle line:90%
She lived through it.

00:34:51.050 --> 00:34:51.883 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Remarkable.

00:34:51.883 --> 00:34:53.975 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: She had an
NDE in which she realized

00:34:53.975 --> 00:34:55.850 align:middle line:84%
that if she chose to
come back to this world,

00:34:55.850 --> 00:34:57.390 align:middle line:90%
her cancer would disappear.

00:34:57.390 --> 00:34:58.970 align:middle line:90%
Which it did.

00:34:58.970 --> 00:35:02.420 align:middle line:84%
We're learning more and more the
power of the nature of spirit,

00:35:02.420 --> 00:35:05.990 align:middle line:84%
the power of prayer, how we
all have a connection with this

00:35:05.990 --> 00:35:08.840 align:middle line:84%
creative force of the universe--
the God force or whatever you

00:35:08.840 --> 00:35:09.740 align:middle line:90%
want to call it--

00:35:09.740 --> 00:35:12.060 align:middle line:84%
the very base of our
conscious awareness.

00:35:12.060 --> 00:35:15.050 align:middle line:84%
And this is how this world
can wake up and become

00:35:15.050 --> 00:35:21.950 align:middle line:84%
a far grander, kinder,
more together world.

00:35:21.950 --> 00:35:24.140 align:middle line:84%
This is the world that
we came here to create.

00:35:24.140 --> 00:35:25.040 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: I agree.

00:35:25.040 --> 00:35:27.740 align:middle line:84%
Eben, Larry Dossey
of "Healing Words"

00:35:27.740 --> 00:35:31.590 align:middle line:84%
talks about the power of prayer
on Gaia's "Inspirations."

00:35:31.590 --> 00:35:32.390 align:middle line:90%
[VIDEO PLAYBACK]

00:35:32.390 --> 00:35:35.000 align:middle line:10%
- I mean, am I denying
my patients something

00:35:35.000 --> 00:35:35.960 align:middle line:10%
that might be helpful?

00:35:35.960 --> 00:35:37.085 align:middle line:10%
- Ah, so are you the block?

00:35:37.085 --> 00:35:39.200 align:middle line:10%
- And I got really
concerned about that.

00:35:39.200 --> 00:35:41.330 align:middle line:10%
The way of resolving
that crisis for me

00:35:41.330 --> 00:35:44.390 align:middle line:10%
was to look at the
world's literature trying

00:35:44.390 --> 00:35:47.570 align:middle line:10%
to find other studies
that had to do with this.

00:35:47.570 --> 00:35:49.670 align:middle line:10%
I thought I might uncover
two or three extra ones

00:35:49.670 --> 00:35:51.080 align:middle line:10%
that I hadn't heard about.

00:35:51.080 --> 00:35:52.790 align:middle line:10%
I came up with a 130.

00:35:52.790 --> 00:35:58.970 align:middle line:10%
And 2/3 of them show that there
is a positive effect from this.

00:35:58.970 --> 00:36:01.220 align:middle line:10%
I began to think this
is the best kept secret

00:36:01.220 --> 00:36:03.150 align:middle line:10%
in modern medicine.

00:36:03.150 --> 00:36:06.660 align:middle line:10%
And so I began to adapt
prayer for all my patients.

00:36:06.660 --> 00:36:10.100 align:middle line:10%
And that's how the book
got published, by the way,

00:36:10.100 --> 00:36:11.840 align:middle line:10%
and written.

00:36:11.840 --> 00:36:13.280 align:middle line:10%
Looking at the data--

00:36:13.280 --> 00:36:15.990 align:middle line:10%
not just stories,
not just anecdotes--

00:36:15.990 --> 00:36:19.940 align:middle line:10%
but combining the scientific
research with the stories

00:36:19.940 --> 00:36:22.750 align:middle line:10%
and that's how "Healing
Words" came to be.

00:36:22.750 --> 00:36:26.360 align:middle line:10%
- And did you pray at the
bedside of these patients?

00:36:26.360 --> 00:36:29.510 align:middle line:10%
- I invented my own
private prayer ritual.

00:36:29.510 --> 00:36:32.870 align:middle line:10%
I would go into my office
early in the morning-- earlier

00:36:32.870 --> 00:36:33.920 align:middle line:10%
than usual.

00:36:33.920 --> 00:36:37.550 align:middle line:10%
Close my door and have my
own private prayer ritual

00:36:37.550 --> 00:36:39.260 align:middle line:10%
that I invented.

00:36:39.260 --> 00:36:40.160 align:middle line:10%
And--

00:36:40.160 --> 00:36:41.030 align:middle line:10%
- Which was?

00:36:41.030 --> 00:36:42.530 align:middle line:10%
- Oh, well, you
really want to know?

00:36:42.530 --> 00:36:43.330 align:middle line:10%
- I do.

00:36:43.330 --> 00:36:44.750 align:middle line:10%
Yes.

00:36:44.750 --> 00:36:47.240 align:middle line:10%
- Well, over the
years, my patients

00:36:47.240 --> 00:36:50.030 align:middle line:10%
knew I was interested in
the anthropology of healing.

00:36:50.030 --> 00:36:54.290 align:middle line:10%
And so they had
given me as gifts

00:36:54.290 --> 00:36:57.890 align:middle line:10%
very shamanic rattles and
various herbal incenses

00:36:57.890 --> 00:36:58.880 align:middle line:10%
from around the world.

00:36:58.880 --> 00:36:59.680 align:middle line:10%
- Interesting.

00:36:59.680 --> 00:37:02.420 align:middle line:10%
- And so I concocted
my own ritual

00:37:02.420 --> 00:37:06.770 align:middle line:10%
where I would burn incense that
shamans and healers were using

00:37:06.770 --> 00:37:09.170 align:middle line:10%
around the world,
and shake my rattles,

00:37:09.170 --> 00:37:13.430 align:middle line:10%
and say my healing request
and prayers for my patients

00:37:13.430 --> 00:37:16.730 align:middle line:10%
that I would be seeing on
hospital rounds that morning

00:37:16.730 --> 00:37:19.010 align:middle line:10%
and who would be coming
to my office that day.

00:37:19.010 --> 00:37:22.790 align:middle line:10%
And I continued
this ritual until I

00:37:22.790 --> 00:37:24.830 align:middle line:10%
retired from the practice
of internal medicine.

00:37:24.830 --> 00:37:25.630 align:middle line:90%
[END PLAYBACK]

00:37:25.630 --> 00:37:27.070 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: It does
work, doesn't it?

00:37:27.070 --> 00:37:28.660 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: It has
tremendous power.

00:37:28.660 --> 00:37:32.590 align:middle line:10%
And along those
lines, I would also

00:37:32.590 --> 00:37:36.010 align:middle line:10%
highly recommend Dr. Larry
Dossey's book, the "One Mind."

00:37:36.010 --> 00:37:39.980 align:middle line:10%
Because he is an identical
twin, and as many people who

00:37:39.980 --> 00:37:42.940 align:middle line:10%
are twins realize telepathy
is absolutely real.

00:37:42.940 --> 00:37:49.270 align:middle line:84%
So he started to investigate
the notion of the connectedness

00:37:49.270 --> 00:37:51.490 align:middle line:84%
of telepathy that's
represented through twins,

00:37:51.490 --> 00:37:53.680 align:middle line:84%
but then expanding
it tremendously

00:37:53.680 --> 00:37:54.820 align:middle line:90%
into the animal world.

00:37:54.820 --> 00:37:57.550 align:middle line:84%
And I won't get into
all of it, but it's

00:37:57.550 --> 00:37:59.725 align:middle line:84%
a wonderful book about the
nature of consciousness.

00:37:59.725 --> 00:38:00.290 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: That's amazing.

00:38:00.290 --> 00:38:02.560 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: But it really
points at the same thing--

00:38:02.560 --> 00:38:04.720 align:middle line:84%
the power of prayer,
the connectedness

00:38:04.720 --> 00:38:06.640 align:middle line:84%
with the conscious
element of the universe.

00:38:06.640 --> 00:38:09.070 align:middle line:84%
It's really just
showing us that there

00:38:09.070 --> 00:38:13.900 align:middle line:84%
are top-down organizational
principles in this world that

00:38:13.900 --> 00:38:17.770 align:middle line:84%
completely help us explain
how all this works.

00:38:17.770 --> 00:38:21.400 align:middle line:84%
That are not the same as
the bottom-up assumptions

00:38:21.400 --> 00:38:22.830 align:middle line:90%
of modern--

00:38:22.830 --> 00:38:28.570 align:middle line:84%
the conventional science that
I studied before my coma, which

00:38:28.570 --> 00:38:31.960 align:middle line:84%
tries to pretend that all
the events in human lives

00:38:31.960 --> 00:38:36.160 align:middle line:84%
are nothing more than electrons,
protons, atoms, molecules.

00:38:36.160 --> 00:38:38.930 align:middle line:84%
All of it just following natural
laws of physics, chemistry,

00:38:38.930 --> 00:38:39.830 align:middle line:90%
biology.

00:38:39.830 --> 00:38:42.370 align:middle line:84%
And that it's all kind of
predictable at the outset,

00:38:42.370 --> 00:38:45.760 align:middle line:84%
and the consciousness emerges
from those physical processes.

00:38:45.760 --> 00:38:48.220 align:middle line:84%
That's why in modern
consciousness studies,

00:38:48.220 --> 00:38:50.590 align:middle line:84%
we realize that's
completely backwards.

00:38:50.590 --> 00:38:53.890 align:middle line:84%
And Dr. Larry Dossey, I think,
is way ahead of the curve,

00:38:53.890 --> 00:38:57.190 align:middle line:84%
as he has been for decades in
showing the power of prayer,

00:38:57.190 --> 00:39:00.040 align:middle line:84%
that it's very real, that
we're spiritual beings, living

00:39:00.040 --> 00:39:02.560 align:middle line:84%
in a spiritual universe,
and that quantum physics

00:39:02.560 --> 00:39:06.010 align:middle line:84%
is one of the most profound
kind of proofs of that.

00:39:06.010 --> 00:39:08.650 align:middle line:84%
But it also shows us
that this world around us

00:39:08.650 --> 00:39:11.290 align:middle line:90%
is not exactly as it appears.

00:39:11.290 --> 00:39:13.810 align:middle line:84%
And that's where it gets
very, very interesting.

00:39:13.810 --> 00:39:17.110 align:middle line:84%
But all of it starts pointing
to the primacy of consciousness

00:39:17.110 --> 00:39:19.510 align:middle line:90%
and the power of our free will.

00:39:19.510 --> 00:39:21.340 align:middle line:84%
Because materialist
science, like

00:39:21.340 --> 00:39:23.170 align:middle line:90%
I worshiped it before my coma--

00:39:23.170 --> 00:39:24.940 align:middle line:84%
and I don't use
that term lightly--

00:39:24.940 --> 00:39:28.660 align:middle line:84%
would have very proudly told
you that you have no such thing

00:39:28.660 --> 00:39:30.310 align:middle line:90%
as free will at all.

00:39:30.310 --> 00:39:33.550 align:middle line:84%
I believe the universe
exists for sentient beings

00:39:33.550 --> 00:39:35.140 align:middle line:90%
to manifest free will.

00:39:35.140 --> 00:39:38.560 align:middle line:84%
That's what that whole evolution
of consciousness is all about.

00:39:38.560 --> 00:39:41.770 align:middle line:84%
So before my coma, like most
of conventional science,

00:39:41.770 --> 00:39:43.990 align:middle line:90%
we had it completely backwards.

00:39:43.990 --> 00:39:46.930 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Had you not had your
near-death experience, Eben,

00:39:46.930 --> 00:39:50.167 align:middle line:84%
would you be where you are
right now in terms of knowledge?

00:39:50.167 --> 00:39:52.250 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: It would've
taken me a little longer,

00:39:52.250 --> 00:39:54.670 align:middle line:84%
but I would have paid
attention to these arguments.

00:39:54.670 --> 00:39:58.390 align:middle line:84%
The logic, the evidence,
the rational argument

00:39:58.390 --> 00:40:00.760 align:middle line:84%
supporting the primacy
of consciousness,

00:40:00.760 --> 00:40:04.090 align:middle line:84%
that we are eternal spiritual
beings in a spiritual universe,

00:40:04.090 --> 00:40:05.030 align:middle line:90%
is overwhelming.

00:40:05.030 --> 00:40:05.830 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: It's huge.

00:40:05.830 --> 00:40:07.288 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: In
fact, what you find

00:40:07.288 --> 00:40:09.460 align:middle line:84%
is most of those people
who claim to be skeptics

00:40:09.460 --> 00:40:11.170 align:middle line:90%
are really pseudo-skeptics.

00:40:11.170 --> 00:40:13.330 align:middle line:84%
They don't even
read the literature,

00:40:13.330 --> 00:40:16.030 align:middle line:84%
because they've made up their
mind that it's impossible

00:40:16.030 --> 00:40:18.220 align:middle line:84%
based on their
theoretical frameworks.

00:40:18.220 --> 00:40:22.030 align:middle line:84%
But their theoretical frameworks
go nowhere on the issue

00:40:22.030 --> 00:40:23.830 align:middle line:90%
of consciousness itself.

00:40:23.830 --> 00:40:25.500 align:middle line:84%
If some materialist
scientist tells you,

00:40:25.500 --> 00:40:27.560 align:middle line:84%
yes, the brain
creates consciousness.

00:40:27.560 --> 00:40:29.030 align:middle line:90%
Well, yes, play along.

00:40:29.030 --> 00:40:30.760 align:middle line:90%
Say yes, well, tell me more.

00:40:30.760 --> 00:40:32.020 align:middle line:90%
You won't get a thing.

00:40:32.020 --> 00:40:33.820 align:middle line:90%
There's nothing there.

00:40:33.820 --> 00:40:36.770 align:middle line:84%
Consciousness is
fundamental and primary.

00:40:36.770 --> 00:40:39.260 align:middle line:84%
And that's why we
have free will.

00:40:39.260 --> 00:40:41.560 align:middle line:90%
We have power over our destiny.

00:40:41.560 --> 00:40:44.950 align:middle line:84%
We have tremendous power
over our very health.

00:40:44.950 --> 00:40:47.890 align:middle line:84%
And that is the most
beautiful lesson

00:40:47.890 --> 00:40:50.350 align:middle line:84%
coming from modern
consciousness studies.

00:40:50.350 --> 00:40:53.020 align:middle line:84%
And I think it's part of
that awakening, that world

00:40:53.020 --> 00:40:57.290 align:middle line:84%
revolution that, in fact, is
essential if we are to survive.

00:40:57.290 --> 00:41:01.300 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Do you think
precognition, telepathy,

00:41:01.300 --> 00:41:02.620 align:middle line:90%
consciousness--

00:41:02.620 --> 00:41:04.060 align:middle line:90%
this is all tied together?

00:41:04.060 --> 00:41:05.560 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: It's
all tied together.

00:41:05.560 --> 00:41:07.510 align:middle line:84%
In fact, it's one
of the big problems

00:41:07.510 --> 00:41:12.340 align:middle line:84%
is so much of our culture
is based in this the world

00:41:12.340 --> 00:41:13.240 align:middle line:90%
of the expert.

00:41:13.240 --> 00:41:14.950 align:middle line:90%
Let's get the expert in.

00:41:14.950 --> 00:41:19.090 align:middle line:84%
Well, it turns out that the
only experts on consciousness

00:41:19.090 --> 00:41:21.643 align:middle line:84%
are people who
study consciousness.

00:41:21.643 --> 00:41:24.310 align:middle line:84%
Studying the brain does not make
you an expert in consciousness.

00:41:24.310 --> 00:41:26.440 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Or who have gone
through things like you have.

00:41:26.440 --> 00:41:27.773 align:middle line:90%
>>ALEXANDER: Well, that is true.

00:41:27.773 --> 00:41:29.710 align:middle line:84%
Or people who have
explored consciousness

00:41:29.710 --> 00:41:32.270 align:middle line:84%
and get to know so
much more about it.

00:41:32.270 --> 00:41:34.690 align:middle line:84%
But I think that's such
a crucial part of this.

00:41:34.690 --> 00:41:37.510 align:middle line:84%
But the experts are
coming into alignment now.

00:41:37.510 --> 00:41:41.140 align:middle line:84%
For example, back in
November, Karen and I

00:41:41.140 --> 00:41:45.430 align:middle line:84%
were in London for the opening
of the Galileo Commission.

00:41:45.430 --> 00:41:49.090 align:middle line:10%
I would advise all of
your viewers to check out

00:41:49.090 --> 00:41:52.660 align:middle line:10%
GalileoCommission.org.

00:41:52.660 --> 00:41:55.810 align:middle line:84%
And more than 100
scientific advisors--

00:41:55.810 --> 00:41:58.540 align:middle line:84%
I'm one of them, but there
are many around the world who

00:41:58.540 --> 00:42:00.940 align:middle line:84%
study consciousness--
and they put out

00:42:00.940 --> 00:42:03.940 align:middle line:84%
this beautiful commission
report that makes it very clear

00:42:03.940 --> 00:42:08.050 align:middle line:84%
that our conventional science
of materialism is dead.

00:42:08.050 --> 00:42:10.390 align:middle line:84%
It actually died
about 80 years ago.

00:42:10.390 --> 00:42:14.620 align:middle line:84%
And this paper is a very
important clarion call

00:42:14.620 --> 00:42:18.100 align:middle line:84%
to this world to wake up to
the fundamental existence

00:42:18.100 --> 00:42:21.640 align:middle line:84%
of consciousness and the power
of our free will over all

00:42:21.640 --> 00:42:23.410 align:middle line:90%
of our evolving future.

00:42:23.410 --> 00:42:28.930 align:middle line:84%
And that we have an important
responsibility in every choice

00:42:28.930 --> 00:42:32.770 align:middle line:84%
we make in our
lives to honor that.

00:42:32.770 --> 00:42:36.670 align:middle line:84%
And that, I think, is probably
one of the biggest lessons.

00:42:36.670 --> 00:42:39.850 align:middle line:84%
Because the materialist science
that I worshipped before that

00:42:39.850 --> 00:42:41.680 align:middle line:84%
would say you have
no free will, they

00:42:41.680 --> 00:42:43.930 align:middle line:84%
say that because
they believe it's

00:42:43.930 --> 00:42:48.320 align:middle line:84%
just the substance, the
brain, the electrons, atoms,

00:42:48.320 --> 00:42:51.350 align:middle line:84%
molecules, following the laws
of physics, chemistry, biology.

00:42:51.350 --> 00:42:54.130 align:middle line:84%
So if it's all just chemical
reactions and electron fluxes,

00:42:54.130 --> 00:42:56.290 align:middle line:84%
where do you insert
any kind of free will?

00:42:56.290 --> 00:42:59.080 align:middle line:84%
And that's where the observer
effect, the lessons of quantum

00:42:59.080 --> 00:43:01.530 align:middle line:84%
physics, modern
consciousness studies

00:43:01.530 --> 00:43:06.640 align:middle line:84%
open the door to a far grander
reality about who we are

00:43:06.640 --> 00:43:09.760 align:middle line:84%
and this awakening and the
nature of consciousness itself.

00:43:09.760 --> 00:43:12.700 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Eben, spiritual
leader Dr. Gary Zukav talks

00:43:12.700 --> 00:43:15.160 align:middle line:90%
about the power of choice.

00:43:15.160 --> 00:43:15.960 align:middle line:90%
[VIDEO PLAYBACK]

00:43:15.960 --> 00:43:19.850 align:middle line:10%
