between you and the life

00:43:19.850 --> 00:43:25.970 align:middle line:10%
that you want of love,
and fulfillment, and joy,

00:43:25.970 --> 00:43:28.400 align:middle line:10%
and appreciation, and
gratitude, and contentment,

00:43:28.400 --> 00:43:31.550 align:middle line:10%
and humbleness, and
clarity, and forgiveness,

00:43:31.550 --> 00:43:35.680 align:middle line:10%
and love are matters of choice--

00:43:35.680 --> 00:43:36.610 align:middle line:10%
your choice.

00:43:36.610 --> 00:43:38.470 align:middle line:10%
And you will see how
powerful your choice

00:43:38.470 --> 00:43:41.530 align:middle line:10%
is when you realize
that you will never

00:43:41.530 --> 00:43:46.210 align:middle line:10%
be judged by the universe
for whatever choice you make,

00:43:46.210 --> 00:43:48.370 align:middle line:10%
because there's learning
in every choice.

00:43:48.370 --> 00:43:49.760 align:middle line:10%
So why choose violence?

00:43:49.760 --> 00:43:57.710 align:middle line:10%
Why choose fear and doubt, when
you can choose love and trust?

00:43:57.710 --> 00:43:59.620 align:middle line:10%
You're on a quest
for authentic power

00:43:59.620 --> 00:44:03.400 align:middle line:10%
and nothing can
prevent that quest.

00:44:03.400 --> 00:44:06.010 align:middle line:10%
Your only choice is the
nature of the experiences

00:44:06.010 --> 00:44:10.060 align:middle line:10%
that you will have
on that quest now.

00:44:10.060 --> 00:44:12.370 align:middle line:10%
And those depend
on your choices.

00:44:12.370 --> 00:44:14.980 align:middle line:10%
This is more than a moral talk.

00:44:14.980 --> 00:44:17.680 align:middle line:10%
This is a talk about evolution.

00:44:17.680 --> 00:44:19.780 align:middle line:10%
Because as you make
those choices--

00:44:19.780 --> 00:44:22.180 align:middle line:10%
choices of love
instead of fear--

00:44:22.180 --> 00:44:32.660 align:middle line:10%
you not only assist in the
maturation of your personality,

00:44:32.660 --> 00:44:34.970 align:middle line:10%
you not only become
capable of giving the gifts

00:44:34.970 --> 00:44:39.290 align:middle line:10%
that you were born to give,
you also assist your soul

00:44:39.290 --> 00:44:40.450 align:middle line:10%
in its evolution.

00:44:40.450 --> 00:44:41.250 align:middle line:90%
[END PLAYBACK]

00:44:41.250 --> 00:44:43.250 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And you write
about the power of choice

00:44:43.250 --> 00:44:44.100 align:middle line:90%
in your latest book.

00:44:44.100 --> 00:44:44.900 align:middle line:90%
>>ALEXANDER: We do.

00:44:44.900 --> 00:44:46.290 align:middle line:90%
And I think it's very important.

00:44:46.290 --> 00:44:48.950 align:middle line:84%
And Gary Zukav is a
good friend, and I

00:44:48.950 --> 00:44:52.550 align:middle line:84%
have been very pleased with
his work, in great agreement.

00:44:52.550 --> 00:44:55.370 align:middle line:84%
I think he shows
us something very

00:44:55.370 --> 00:44:57.320 align:middle line:84%
deep about that power
of choice and how

00:44:57.320 --> 00:44:59.000 align:middle line:90%
we are truly responsible.

00:44:59.000 --> 00:45:01.010 align:middle line:84%
And I think what
near-death experiences

00:45:01.010 --> 00:45:03.470 align:middle line:84%
would supplement
that notion with is

00:45:03.470 --> 00:45:05.480 align:middle line:90%
it's not just our actions.

00:45:05.480 --> 00:45:07.490 align:middle line:84%
Because when you go through
a life review, which

00:45:07.490 --> 00:45:11.150 align:middle line:84%
has been very commonly described
in near-death experiences going

00:45:11.150 --> 00:45:15.110 align:middle line:84%
back at least 2,400 years
to the time of Plato,

00:45:15.110 --> 00:45:17.420 align:middle line:84%
what you realize
in the life review

00:45:17.420 --> 00:45:20.610 align:middle line:84%
is that even your
thoughts have an impact.

00:45:20.610 --> 00:45:21.990 align:middle line:84%
That's why it's
so important to--

00:45:21.990 --> 00:45:23.540 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: You're right.

00:45:23.540 --> 00:45:25.280 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: --be
mindful of what

00:45:25.280 --> 00:45:29.030 align:middle line:84%
we're thinking, and our
thoughts and our emotions.

00:45:29.030 --> 00:45:34.280 align:middle line:84%
Because the life review shows
very clearly, as so many

00:45:34.280 --> 00:45:38.450 align:middle line:84%
describe it, that you
experience it not as yourself.

00:45:38.450 --> 00:45:41.420 align:middle line:84%
You experience it
as those around you

00:45:41.420 --> 00:45:44.570 align:middle line:84%
who were impacted by your
thoughts and actions.

00:45:44.570 --> 00:45:47.030 align:middle line:84%
It's a beautiful
example of showing us

00:45:47.030 --> 00:45:49.580 align:middle line:84%
that we are not our little
self and our little ego,

00:45:49.580 --> 00:45:51.530 align:middle line:84%
but that, in fact, we
are part of that far

00:45:51.530 --> 00:45:53.160 align:middle line:90%
grander consciousness.

00:45:53.160 --> 00:45:56.390 align:middle line:84%
And this is all about the
dream of that primordial mind.

00:45:56.390 --> 00:45:59.750 align:middle line:84%
It is working through all
this in a very active fashion.

00:45:59.750 --> 00:46:04.430 align:middle line:84%
But each and every one of us
is learning in that process

00:46:04.430 --> 00:46:08.190 align:middle line:84%
through our relationships with
others and acknowledging--

00:46:08.190 --> 00:46:11.930 align:middle line:84%
because in the life review, any
pain or suffering that you've

00:46:11.930 --> 00:46:14.637 align:middle line:84%
handed out to others,
you will feel,

00:46:14.637 --> 00:46:16.095 align:middle line:84%
you will have the
emotional impact.

00:46:16.095 --> 00:46:17.540 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: It comes
back, doesn't it?

00:46:17.540 --> 00:46:19.873 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: You talked a
little while ago about Hitler.

00:46:19.873 --> 00:46:21.980 align:middle line:84%
I would not envy
that life review.

00:46:21.980 --> 00:46:23.970 align:middle line:90%
More than 53 million deaths.

00:46:23.970 --> 00:46:24.770 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Yes.

00:46:24.770 --> 00:46:26.312 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: Not to
mention all those

00:46:26.312 --> 00:46:30.800 align:middle line:84%
impacted by the actions
of him with that war.

00:46:30.800 --> 00:46:32.960 align:middle line:84%
His life review
would be incredible.

00:46:32.960 --> 00:46:34.370 align:middle line:90%
What a learning experience.

00:46:34.370 --> 00:46:38.270 align:middle line:84%
But he had to experience every
bit of that pain and suffering.

00:46:38.270 --> 00:46:39.650 align:middle line:90%
We reap what we sow.

00:46:39.650 --> 00:46:42.950 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Do you think he has
reincarnated and is getting

00:46:42.950 --> 00:46:47.370 align:middle line:84%
better or do you think he has
been put in fire and brimstone?

00:46:47.370 --> 00:46:50.150 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: No, I--
first of all, it's

00:46:50.150 --> 00:46:53.150 align:middle line:84%
important to point
out that Earth time is

00:46:53.150 --> 00:46:54.800 align:middle line:90%
part of the stage setting.

00:46:54.800 --> 00:46:57.992 align:middle line:84%
So in other words, when you say,
has he already reincarnated,

00:46:57.992 --> 00:47:00.200 align:middle line:84%
it's a question that really
doesn't have much meaning

00:47:00.200 --> 00:47:02.850 align:middle line:84%
when you consider that there
is a temporal flow, that I call

00:47:02.850 --> 00:47:05.660 align:middle line:84%
deep time, in the
spiritual realm that

00:47:05.660 --> 00:47:09.320 align:middle line:84%
is much more of an alignment
of our lessons learned

00:47:09.320 --> 00:47:10.430 align:middle line:90%
and our journeys.

00:47:10.430 --> 00:47:12.800 align:middle line:84%
And so, by definition,
nobody ever

00:47:12.800 --> 00:47:16.770 align:middle line:84%
reincarnates before they
had to be present there

00:47:16.770 --> 00:47:18.800 align:middle line:84%
for all loved ones
and others who were

00:47:18.800 --> 00:47:21.140 align:middle line:90%
crossing over-- what have you.

00:47:21.140 --> 00:47:24.300 align:middle line:84%
There is a deeper
ordering of causality.

00:47:24.300 --> 00:47:27.560 align:middle line:84%
So all I can say is that
Hitler's life review would not

00:47:27.560 --> 00:47:30.260 align:middle line:84%
be anything that I think Hitler
would want to go through,

00:47:30.260 --> 00:47:34.850 align:middle line:84%
but he chose that for his
own pathway, his higher soul.

00:47:34.850 --> 00:47:37.310 align:middle line:84%
And I'm not one to
sit here and define

00:47:37.310 --> 00:47:39.260 align:middle line:84%
how we can explain
all the depths

00:47:39.260 --> 00:47:42.530 align:middle line:84%
of evil and apparent darkness
we've seen in this world.

00:47:42.530 --> 00:47:46.490 align:middle line:84%
But I do believe that they all
are there for a purpose to help

00:47:46.490 --> 00:47:49.345 align:middle line:84%
to guide us towards that
oneness, towards love,

00:47:49.345 --> 00:47:50.720 align:middle line:84%
just as near-death
experiencers--

00:47:50.720 --> 00:47:53.300 align:middle line:84%
people who have been to that
other side and then come back

00:47:53.300 --> 00:47:55.070 align:middle line:90%
to this world to talk about it--

00:47:55.070 --> 00:47:57.230 align:middle line:90%
share the importance of that.

00:47:57.230 --> 00:47:59.960 align:middle line:84%
When we see the
good side of humans

00:47:59.960 --> 00:48:03.410 align:middle line:84%
in dealing with hardships,
whether it's a natural disaster

00:48:03.410 --> 00:48:08.450 align:middle line:84%
or human on human conflict, we
see beautiful examples of love,

00:48:08.450 --> 00:48:12.260 align:middle line:84%
of unconditional love,
being the overwhelming force

00:48:12.260 --> 00:48:13.442 align:middle line:90%
in the equation.

00:48:13.442 --> 00:48:14.900 align:middle line:84%
And I would say
that that is really

00:48:14.900 --> 00:48:17.030 align:middle line:90%
the deepest lesson of all this.

00:48:17.030 --> 00:48:19.850 align:middle line:90%
And as much as people--

00:48:19.850 --> 00:48:22.280 align:middle line:84%
it can become
overwhelming if you

00:48:22.280 --> 00:48:24.020 align:middle line:90%
dwell on the darkness and evil.

00:48:24.020 --> 00:48:25.850 align:middle line:84%
But if you can rise
above it a bit--

00:48:25.850 --> 00:48:30.650 align:middle line:84%
and this is why I often repeat
those words that I first said

00:48:30.650 --> 00:48:31.760 align:middle line:90%
when I came out of coma--

00:48:31.760 --> 00:48:33.110 align:middle line:84%
I don't remember
saying these words,

00:48:33.110 --> 00:48:34.640 align:middle line:84%
but everybody at
the bedside told me

00:48:34.640 --> 00:48:36.260 align:middle line:90%
I said it over and over again--

00:48:36.260 --> 00:48:38.660 align:middle line:90%
all is well.

00:48:38.660 --> 00:48:40.440 align:middle line:90%
All is well.

00:48:40.440 --> 00:48:43.010 align:middle line:84%
And what that really means
is when you meditate,

00:48:43.010 --> 00:48:46.250 align:middle line:84%
go into this, develop this
relationship with higher soul,

00:48:46.250 --> 00:48:50.150 align:middle line:84%
you start to get the big
broad overall view that

00:48:50.150 --> 00:48:54.080 align:middle line:84%
incorporates all of it, and
can see a win-win situation.

00:48:54.080 --> 00:48:56.390 align:middle line:84%
I came to see that some
people who before my coma

00:48:56.390 --> 00:48:59.160 align:middle line:84%
I looked at as my nemesis,
as an enemy, someone who

00:48:59.160 --> 00:49:01.250 align:middle line:84%
is preventing me from
getting things in my life

00:49:01.250 --> 00:49:04.670 align:middle line:84%
that I wanted, in fact,
was a near and dear soul

00:49:04.670 --> 00:49:07.120 align:middle line:84%
mate who was helping me
to learn a tough lesson.

00:49:07.120 --> 00:49:07.920 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Wow.

00:49:07.920 --> 00:49:09.410 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: We're
all in this together.

00:49:09.410 --> 00:49:10.452 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: That's dramatic.

00:49:10.452 --> 00:49:12.920 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: So always try to
take that bigger, higher view

00:49:12.920 --> 00:49:15.470 align:middle line:84%
where you can see how love
really connects us all.

00:49:15.470 --> 00:49:18.860 align:middle line:84%
And even those who seem to be
bringing badness into our lives

00:49:18.860 --> 00:49:23.270 align:middle line:84%
or into the world, in some ways
are helping us to examine more

00:49:23.270 --> 00:49:25.910 align:middle line:84%
deeply and come up with
something that makes

00:49:25.910 --> 00:49:29.730 align:middle line:84%
more sense about connectedness,
and purpose, and growth

00:49:29.730 --> 00:49:33.690 align:middle line:84%
towards this oneness, towards
what Teilhard de Chardin was

00:49:33.690 --> 00:49:34.620 align:middle line:90%
discussing.

00:49:34.620 --> 00:49:36.397 align:middle line:84%
And that's where
this is all headed.

00:49:36.397 --> 00:49:37.980 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Would I
have liked you before

00:49:37.980 --> 00:49:39.787 align:middle line:90%
your near-death experience?

00:49:39.787 --> 00:49:40.870 align:middle line:90%
>>ALEXANDER: I don't know.

00:49:40.870 --> 00:49:41.650 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: What do you think?

00:49:41.650 --> 00:49:42.460 align:middle line:90%
>>ALEXANDER: I think.

00:49:42.460 --> 00:49:43.260 align:middle line:90%
I mean--

00:49:43.260 --> 00:49:45.608 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Did you like you?

00:49:45.608 --> 00:49:46.650 align:middle line:90%
>>ALEXANDER: Yeah, I did.

00:49:46.650 --> 00:49:49.710 align:middle line:84%
I liked me, but I had a
lot of growing up to do.

00:49:49.710 --> 00:49:55.890 align:middle line:84%
I mean, especially, I would
say as I evolved beyond my NDE,

00:49:55.890 --> 00:49:57.990 align:middle line:84%
and took on this much
broader view of self,

00:49:57.990 --> 00:50:01.770 align:middle line:84%
and my role in my life,
and started doing past life

00:50:01.770 --> 00:50:03.570 align:middle line:84%
regressions, and getting
some kind of idea

00:50:03.570 --> 00:50:09.210 align:middle line:84%
of the context in which I might
actually be an eternal spirit.

00:50:09.210 --> 00:50:11.190 align:middle line:84%
It's always a case
of all is well.

00:50:11.190 --> 00:50:14.550 align:middle line:84%
I think the key is you need to
be able to realize that bigger

00:50:14.550 --> 00:50:17.940 align:middle line:84%
picture and how all this has
a positive direction in it.

00:50:17.940 --> 00:50:19.740 align:middle line:84%
When we talk about
reincarnation,

00:50:19.740 --> 00:50:21.990 align:middle line:84%
it's not the blind
mechanistic wheel

00:50:21.990 --> 00:50:23.550 align:middle line:90%
of some religious systems.

00:50:23.550 --> 00:50:26.220 align:middle line:90%
It's very much goal-directed.

00:50:26.220 --> 00:50:29.640 align:middle line:84%
And it's towards
that sense of love,

00:50:29.640 --> 00:50:32.520 align:middle line:84%
and of prosperity
for all, and of true

00:50:32.520 --> 00:50:34.080 align:middle line:90%
brotherhood and sisterhood.

00:50:34.080 --> 00:50:36.300 align:middle line:84%
And not only that, but
realizing that this is not

00:50:36.300 --> 00:50:38.080 align:middle line:90%
just about humans at all.

00:50:38.080 --> 00:50:41.070 align:middle line:84%
It's about all life
throughout the cosmos.

00:50:41.070 --> 00:50:44.130 align:middle line:84%
It's a much bigger
deal than we currently

00:50:44.130 --> 00:50:49.920 align:middle line:84%
can discern from our limited
materialistic four-dimensional

00:50:49.920 --> 00:50:51.120 align:middle line:90%
space time view.

00:50:51.120 --> 00:50:53.130 align:middle line:84%
But that's why
exploring consciousness

00:50:53.130 --> 00:50:56.700 align:middle line:84%
and developing a much richer
relationship with our higher

00:50:56.700 --> 00:50:59.010 align:middle line:84%
soul, with that
primordial mind, is

00:50:59.010 --> 00:51:01.830 align:middle line:84%
so crucial in our
personal growth,

00:51:01.830 --> 00:51:05.370 align:middle line:84%
and also in the evolution of
all of life in the universe,

00:51:05.370 --> 00:51:08.640 align:middle line:84%
and certainly, of humanity's
coming into its own

00:51:08.640 --> 00:51:09.515 align:middle line:90%
in the current era.

00:51:09.515 --> 00:51:10.890 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Are you
afraid of dying?

00:51:10.890 --> 00:51:12.120 align:middle line:90%
>>ALEXANDER: Not at all.

00:51:12.120 --> 00:51:14.190 align:middle line:90%
Dying is an adventure.

00:51:14.190 --> 00:51:15.420 align:middle line:90%
It is a release from--

00:51:15.420 --> 00:51:16.220 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: No rush.

00:51:16.220 --> 00:51:17.387 align:middle line:90%
>>ALEXANDER: --the shackles.

00:51:17.387 --> 00:51:18.710 align:middle line:90%
I'm in no rush now.

00:51:18.710 --> 00:51:22.150 align:middle line:84%
I believe I still have much
work to do in this world.

00:51:22.150 --> 00:51:22.950 align:middle line:90%
I believe--

00:51:22.950 --> 00:51:23.750 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Me too.

00:51:23.750 --> 00:51:27.540 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: --for one
thing I can't remotely claim

00:51:27.540 --> 00:51:30.060 align:middle line:84%
to have a perfect
understanding of this primacy

00:51:30.060 --> 00:51:31.710 align:middle line:84%
of consciousness,
the primordial mind

00:51:31.710 --> 00:51:35.250 align:middle line:84%
hypotheses that we explore in
"Living in a Mindful Universe,"

00:51:35.250 --> 00:51:38.040 align:middle line:84%
but I certainly can see the
direction in which it's headed.

00:51:38.040 --> 00:51:43.110 align:middle line:84%
And for me that direction
absolutely depends on science,

00:51:43.110 --> 00:51:46.530 align:middle line:84%
because science is the way
that we share information

00:51:46.530 --> 00:51:49.690 align:middle line:84%
and we come to what's
known as consilience.

00:51:49.690 --> 00:51:52.710 align:middle line:84%
Consilience is basically
a statement that,

00:51:52.710 --> 00:51:55.350 align:middle line:84%
when you examine a
certain profound problem

00:51:55.350 --> 00:51:58.140 align:middle line:84%
from very different
directions, if they all

00:51:58.140 --> 00:52:01.050 align:middle line:84%
start converging on the
same thing, that is what

00:52:01.050 --> 00:52:02.890 align:middle line:90%
we should discern as truth.

00:52:02.890 --> 00:52:05.250 align:middle line:84%
And just to cut to
the chase, I would

00:52:05.250 --> 00:52:10.530 align:middle line:84%
like to say in this discussion
consilience synthesizes two

00:52:10.530 --> 00:52:12.910 align:middle line:84%
of most profound mysteries
to modern science.

00:52:12.910 --> 00:52:17.010 align:middle line:84%
One is the measurement
paradox, observer effect,

00:52:17.010 --> 00:52:20.550 align:middle line:84%
what's known as contextually
in quantum physics.

00:52:20.550 --> 00:52:22.950 align:middle line:84%
And the other is the
mind/brain connection as

00:52:22.950 --> 00:52:25.680 align:middle line:84%
examined through neuroscience
and philosophy of mind.

00:52:25.680 --> 00:52:28.200 align:middle line:84%
And it turns out that
a fascinating example

00:52:28.200 --> 00:52:31.140 align:middle line:84%
of consilience is how
both of those very

00:52:31.140 --> 00:52:35.520 align:middle line:84%
broad, deep examinations
of the nature of reality

00:52:35.520 --> 00:52:38.280 align:middle line:84%
by very intelligent
insightful people

00:52:38.280 --> 00:52:41.790 align:middle line:84%
are all leading to the same
conclusion of the primacy

00:52:41.790 --> 00:52:46.440 align:middle line:84%
of mind and the power
we have to manifest

00:52:46.440 --> 00:52:47.970 align:middle line:90%
the world of our dreams.

00:52:47.970 --> 00:52:50.400 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: It is
amazing how it works.

00:52:50.400 --> 00:52:53.380 align:middle line:84%
It seems complex, but it's
very simple, isn't it?

00:52:53.380 --> 00:52:54.180 align:middle line:90%
>>ALEXANDER: It is.

00:52:54.180 --> 00:52:57.420 align:middle line:84%
It is absolutely
beautifully simple.

00:52:57.420 --> 00:53:01.260 align:middle line:84%
When you can summarize it
in the phrase "all is well"

00:53:01.260 --> 00:53:03.540 align:middle line:84%
and fully understand
what that means,

00:53:03.540 --> 00:53:05.850 align:middle line:84%
come to realize that
things like life reviews

00:53:05.850 --> 00:53:08.340 align:middle line:84%
just show us that
the golden rule--

00:53:08.340 --> 00:53:11.610 align:middle line:84%
do unto others as you would
have done unto yourself--

00:53:11.610 --> 00:53:15.400 align:middle line:84%
is written into the very
fabric of the universe.

00:53:15.400 --> 00:53:18.900 align:middle line:84%
And as we come to acknowledge
these deep and profound lessons

00:53:18.900 --> 00:53:21.660 align:middle line:84%
in a scientific sense,
the spiritual nature

00:53:21.660 --> 00:53:24.330 align:middle line:84%
of our very being
and of this universe,

00:53:24.330 --> 00:53:25.798 align:middle line:90%
we will grow tremendously.

00:53:25.798 --> 00:53:27.840 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: I want you to
assume for a moment, Eben,

00:53:27.840 --> 00:53:30.570 align:middle line:84%
that you are standing
at the deathbed of one

00:53:30.570 --> 00:53:32.370 align:middle line:90%
of your patients.

00:53:32.370 --> 00:53:34.110 align:middle line:90%
The time has come.

00:53:34.110 --> 00:53:36.250 align:middle line:90%
What do you tell them now?

00:53:36.250 --> 00:53:39.660 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: What I tell
them is that what they

00:53:39.660 --> 00:53:43.380 align:middle line:84%
are about to witness is
the most beautiful example

00:53:43.380 --> 00:53:47.340 align:middle line:84%
of the connectedness of
souls throughout the cosmos,

00:53:47.340 --> 00:53:50.160 align:middle line:84%
of connectedness with the
very prime creative force

00:53:50.160 --> 00:53:53.310 align:middle line:84%
of this universe, and that
they will find greater love

00:53:53.310 --> 00:53:56.190 align:middle line:84%
and comfort than
they've ever witnessed

00:53:56.190 --> 00:53:59.310 align:middle line:84%
in this four-dimensional
incarnation, unless, of course,

00:53:59.310 --> 00:54:02.220 align:middle line:84%
they developed a very active
practice of going within.

00:54:02.220 --> 00:54:04.680 align:middle line:84%
Because you can certainly
come to see this,

00:54:04.680 --> 00:54:07.320 align:middle line:84%
know this, through being
open-minded, and living

00:54:07.320 --> 00:54:12.840 align:middle line:84%
these lives, and seeing the
love, the power of forgiveness

00:54:12.840 --> 00:54:16.290 align:middle line:84%
and acceptance and mercy on
all fellow beings beginning

00:54:16.290 --> 00:54:19.170 align:middle line:84%
with that soul
that you know best.

00:54:19.170 --> 00:54:22.890 align:middle line:84%
This is all about coming into
greater discovery of that.

00:54:22.890 --> 00:54:25.440 align:middle line:84%
The one thing I would
assure them of--

00:54:25.440 --> 00:54:28.380 align:middle line:90%
and I'm most assuring of this--

00:54:28.380 --> 00:54:31.470 align:middle line:84%
is that when you die,
your conscious awareness

00:54:31.470 --> 00:54:33.543 align:middle line:90%
becomes far grander.

00:54:33.543 --> 00:54:34.710 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: That's interesting.

00:54:34.710 --> 00:54:36.665 align:middle line:84%
Why don't we teach
this in school?

00:54:36.665 --> 00:54:38.040 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: Well,
I mean, that's

00:54:38.040 --> 00:54:41.370 align:middle line:84%
what we're trying to do is
bring this reality to the world.

00:54:41.370 --> 00:54:45.210 align:middle line:84%
Luckily, what I see in this
world in the last decade

00:54:45.210 --> 00:54:48.690 align:middle line:84%
is a tremendous amount of
growth along these lines.

00:54:48.690 --> 00:54:52.660 align:middle line:84%
I cannot tell you how many
scientists, engineers,

00:54:52.660 --> 00:54:58.380 align:middle line:84%
modern scientifically-educated
people contact me and are very

00:54:58.380 --> 00:55:03.510 align:middle line:84%
grateful for the big view that
this kind of thinking brings

00:55:03.510 --> 00:55:05.080 align:middle line:90%
them.

00:55:05.080 --> 00:55:08.430 align:middle line:84%
And it really is
all about all of us

00:55:08.430 --> 00:55:10.500 align:middle line:84%
coming to greater
knowing of self

00:55:10.500 --> 00:55:14.520 align:middle line:84%
and of others and of these
very deep principles.

00:55:14.520 --> 00:55:17.940 align:middle line:84%
It's wisdom that's been in this
world for thousands of years.

00:55:17.940 --> 00:55:19.140 align:middle line:90%
Go back to Vedic texts.

00:55:19.140 --> 00:55:22.870 align:middle line:84%
Go back to eastern and
western spiritual origins,

00:55:22.870 --> 00:55:25.530 align:middle line:84%
the original
teachings of prophets.

00:55:25.530 --> 00:55:29.170 align:middle line:84%
I mean, so many of them glimpsed
this, knew this, felt this,

00:55:29.170 --> 00:55:31.950 align:middle line:84%
were co-creating
it even back then.

00:55:31.950 --> 00:55:36.420 align:middle line:84%
So in so many ways, it's
not like this is big news.

00:55:36.420 --> 00:55:38.160 align:middle line:90%
But it really is--

00:55:38.160 --> 00:55:41.550 align:middle line:84%
I would say it's the
culmination of the 400

00:55:41.550 --> 00:55:44.040 align:middle line:84%
years of the scientific
revolution trying

00:55:44.040 --> 00:55:46.230 align:middle line:84%
to make sense of this
world in a way that

00:55:46.230 --> 00:55:48.960 align:middle line:84%
goes beyond personal
experience and just what

00:55:48.960 --> 00:55:52.115 align:middle line:84%
an individual could discern
from their own life experience.

00:55:52.115 --> 00:55:53.490 align:middle line:84%
But we really need
to know what's

00:55:53.490 --> 00:55:56.140 align:middle line:90%
the bigger human experience.

00:55:56.140 --> 00:55:59.310 align:middle line:84%
What can we all truly share
about the nature of reality?

00:55:59.310 --> 00:56:02.400 align:middle line:84%
And that's why I think this
kind of awakening is so crucial.

00:56:02.400 --> 00:56:05.017 align:middle line:10%
Now, of course, it
also, as I said earlier,

00:56:05.017 --> 00:56:06.600 align:middle line:10%
it's part of that
gift of desperation,

00:56:06.600 --> 00:56:10.860 align:middle line:10%
because the status quo,
the economic polarization--

00:56:10.860 --> 00:56:14.610 align:middle line:10%
the wealth is far, far,
far too concentrated

00:56:14.610 --> 00:56:18.270 align:middle line:10%
in a tiny pocket in this
country and around this world.

00:56:18.270 --> 00:56:22.590 align:middle line:10%
we really need to have a far
grander vision of sharing

00:56:22.590 --> 00:56:24.360 align:middle line:10%
and of taking care
of each other,

00:56:24.360 --> 00:56:27.630 align:middle line:10%
taking care of the least,
the last, and the lost,

00:56:27.630 --> 00:56:30.330 align:middle line:10%
realizing we're all
in this together.

00:56:30.330 --> 00:56:32.100 align:middle line:84%
And that the only
thing that is important

00:56:32.100 --> 00:56:34.290 align:middle line:90%
really is our soul journey.

00:56:34.290 --> 00:56:36.710 align:middle line:10%
And in the soul journey, as
any near-death experiencer

00:56:36.710 --> 00:56:39.640 align:middle line:10%
will tell you, you never
go through it and think,

00:56:39.640 --> 00:56:42.698 align:middle line:10%
well, I should have had
a Porsche or a yacht.

00:56:42.698 --> 00:56:44.490 align:middle line:84%
That would have made
my life more complete.

00:56:44.490 --> 00:56:45.290 align:middle line:90%
No.

00:56:45.290 --> 00:56:46.690 align:middle line:90%
It's about the relationships.

00:56:46.690 --> 00:56:47.920 align:middle line:90%
It's about the love.

00:56:47.920 --> 00:56:50.970 align:middle line:84%
It's about the power that
comes from helping others.

00:56:50.970 --> 00:56:53.070 align:middle line:84%
And realizing that
that's the best

00:56:53.070 --> 00:56:57.240 align:middle line:84%
way to essentially
concentrate focus

00:56:57.240 --> 00:56:59.400 align:middle line:84%
and resonate with
this beautiful love

00:56:59.400 --> 00:57:01.590 align:middle line:84%
that the creator
has of the creation,

00:57:01.590 --> 00:57:05.220 align:middle line:84%
that we can each come to
know in our own existence

00:57:05.220 --> 00:57:07.140 align:middle line:84%
simply through
opening our minds,

00:57:07.140 --> 00:57:10.440 align:middle line:84%
feeling the emotional power
of all this, and yet, also,

00:57:10.440 --> 00:57:13.440 align:middle line:84%
developing that relationship
with our higher soul, which

00:57:13.440 --> 00:57:15.428 align:middle line:84%
is one of connectedness
and purpose.

00:57:15.428 --> 00:57:16.470 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Eben, thank you.

00:57:16.470 --> 00:57:20.130 align:middle line:10%
Not only for being on "Beyond
Belief," but for sharing

00:57:20.130 --> 00:57:22.120 align:middle line:10%
truly a remarkable
story of your life.

00:57:22.120 --> 00:57:22.920 align:middle line:90%
I appreciate it.

00:57:22.920 --> 00:57:24.462 align:middle line:84%
>>ALEXANDER: Well,
thank you, George.

00:57:24.462 --> 00:57:26.760 align:middle line:84%
It's always a pleasure to
talk with you and thanks

00:57:26.760 --> 00:57:28.470 align:middle line:90%
so much for having me back.

00:57:28.470 --> 00:57:31.260 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Dr. Eben Alexander,
our remarkable guest here

00:57:31.260 --> 00:57:32.340 align:middle line:90%
on "Beyond Belief."

00:57:32.340 --> 00:57:35.610 align:middle line:84%
If you've ever doubted the
possibility of the existence

00:57:35.610 --> 00:57:38.580 align:middle line:84%
of the other side,
don't doubt it any more

00:57:38.580 --> 00:57:40.020 align:middle line:90%
when you listen to him.

00:57:40.020 --> 00:57:42.420 align:middle line:84%
Thanks for watching
"Beyond Belief."

